705332f-a.title: Brooklyn: Knickerbocker Avenue - Covert Street
705332f-a.text:
834-844 Knickerbocker Ave., south side, between Covert and Schaeffer
Streets. No. 840 is the remodeled frame house in the center of the view.
March 1923.
